processingCommand.script:
:PRINT "RESTORE COMPLETED"
:SET &RESTORE_COMPLETED# = "true"
:PUBLISH &RESTORE_COMPLETED#,,TOP

!:SET &JOBNR#  = SYS_ACT_PARENT_NR()
!:READ &JOBNR#,,,&JOBNR#
!:SET &TASKNR# = GET_UC_OBJECT_NR("PREPARE-CONTINUE.UPGRADE.DSC-WM-LATAM.S")
!:READ &TASKNR#,,,&TASKNR#
!:SET &STATUS# = MODIFY_UC_OBJECT(&JOBNR#, RELEASE, &TASKNR#)

!:SET &WMSNR#  = GET_UC_OBJECT_NR("MODULE-WMS.UPGRADE.DSC-WM-LATAM.WST")
!:SET &REFSNR# = GET_UC_OBJECT_NR("MODULE-REFS.UPGRADE.DSC-WM-LATAM.WST")
!:SET &RWNR#   = GET_UC_OBJECT_NR("MODULE-RW.UPGRADE.DSC-WM-LATAM.WST")
!:SET &EMSNR#  = GET_UC_OBJECT_NR("MODULE-EMS.UPGRADE.DSC-WM-LATAM.WST")

:SET &WMSNR#  = ${MODULE_WMS_ID#}
:SET &REFSNR# = ${MODULE_REFS_ID#}
:SET &RWNR#   = ${MODULE_RW_ID#}
:SET &EMSNR#  = ${MODULE_EMS_ID#}

:P &WMSNR#  
:P &REFSNR# 
:P &RWNR#  
:P &EMSNR#  

!:SET &RET#    = CANCEL_UC_OBJECT(&WMSNR#, "ENDED_CANCEL")
!:SET &RET#    = CANCEL_UC_OBJECT(&REFSNR#, "ENDED_CANCEL")
!:SET &RET#    = CANCEL_UC_OBJECT(&RWNR#, "ENDED_CANCEL")
!:SET &RET#    = CANCEL_UC_OBJECT(&EMSNR#, "ENDED_CANCEL")
